data.description: EXPANSIVE THREE-BEDROOM RESIDENCE WITH TWO AND A HALF BATHS, TWO SPACIOUS LIVING AREAS, AN OFFICE, AND A MEDIA ROOM. THE KITCHEN BOASTS ELEGANT GRANITE COUNTERTOPS AND STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES. THE MASTER SUITE OFFERS DUAL SINKS, A SEPARATE SHOWER, AND A BATHTUB. THE PROPERTY INCLUDES A SIZABLE BACKYARD COMPLETE WITH A STORAGE SHED. HOUSE NEEDS FOUNDATION REPAIR. IT WILL BE REPAIRED PRIOR TO CLOSING WITH A LIFETIME TRANSFERRABLE WARRANTY. SEE FOUNDATION REPORT IN DOCUMENTS. NO BLIND OFFERS WILL BE CONSIDERED.
